AddressInfo.Title: East Rand Mall (Boksburg)
AddressInfo.AddressLine1: Benthal Rd, Jansenpark, Alberton, Gauteng, South Africa, 1459
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Primary Entry Point	
Enter through the booths, turn left towards the parking area and continue with the road to turn left towards the ramp. Continue with the road from the ramp onwards.. When you reach an open parking area, be sure to turn to your left to go down another ramp. Turn right and right again, the charge point will be visible in front of you.
Secondary Entry Point	
Enter through the booth, continue straight and then turn right up the ramp and then to your left. Turn right and continue straight to turn left and following the road down the ramp. Turn then to your right, take another right. The charge point will be visible in front of you.

GeneralComments: With 180 stores to browse, there is no better way to spend your time while charging your EV. Our DC fast charger is situated in the undercover parking near Entrance 2 and 3.
